name: David Perez
text: Ordered a smoothie that I felt didn’t taste very good, didn’t taste like anything to be honest. Took two sips and knew I wanted my money back. Cashier tells me “that’s what you ordered and that’s how it tastes”....said they were not in charge and couldn’t give me a refund.

name: Neel Patel
text: I ordered cheese cake was very dry
